faqs.question: How do I get started with Phoenix Cloud?
faqs.answer: Simply choose a plan that fits your needs, click 'Order Now', and you'll be redirected to our website from where you can setup your server within minutes.

faqs.question: What payment methods do you accept?
faqs.answer: We accept various payment methods including PayPal, credit/debit cards, and cryptocurrency. Contact our sales team on Discord for more details.

faqs.question: What is your uptime guarantee?
faqs.answer: We offer a 99.9% uptime SLA across all our hosting plans. If we fail to meet this guarantee, you'll receive service credits as compensation.

faqs.question: Do you offer DDoS protection?
faqs.answer: Yes, all our plans include enterprise-grade DDoS protection at no extra cost. Our network can mitigate attacks up to 1Tbps.

faqs.question: Can I upgrade my plan later?
faqs.answer: Absolutely! You can upgrade your plan at any time. Our team will help migrate your services with minimal downtime.

faqs.question: What kind of support do you offer?
faqs.answer: We provide 24/7 support through Discord. Our expert team is always ready to help with any technical issues or questions.
